room_title: Escape room "Stranger Times " by Escape Challenge St. Louis in St. Louis
room_description:
The world has nearly been destroyed by the Upside Down’s evil creatures.

The human race is on the edge of extinction.  HOWEVER, a time machine has been discovered to get you to Hawkins Indiana 1984, where things first got STRANGE. 

This is humanity’s last chance to be saved! Can you do it before the creatures reach us in 60 minutes?
